    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the \"long term\" thing but for a small shop owner just trying to keep the lights on right now, those \"short term burdens\" are pretty huge. do u think the innovation part actually happens for them, or does it just end up being an excuse for more red tape and higher prices for customers?",
